data.description: Introducing an exceptional energy-efficient home, perfectly positioned on a prominent corner lot! Providing a 2-car with an extended driveway and an RV gate. The welcoming living room invites you to relax, while the formal dining room stands ready for holding elegant dinners. In the desirable family room, you'll find a floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace and sliding glass doors to the back patio. The galley kitchen features recessed lighting, built-in appliances, espresso cabinetry, and a breakfast nook. The main bedroom is a sanctuary of comfort, complete with direct outdoor access, a walk-in closet, and a bathroom with dual sinks. Be surprised by the delightful backyard boasting a covered patio, citrus trees, and a refreshing pool...
